name: reincarnations, same lives
description:
with all the good times i've willed into existence up from my lack of self restraint, you'd think it wouldn't culminate into all this sadness.

-

november 10th, 2021
strange times, we’re all
reincarnations of our
past selves into what
isn’t necessarily worse,
but tell me around here 
where times are getting better
i just need a fucking signal
my newly formed cells
won’t have to repeat that
old shit;
live that same life
again.

-

@literallynft
